  "text": "The proof of Theorem 3.4 is considerably more involved than that of Theorem 3.2. In particular, it uses the following lemma, due to Rossman [CITATION_1] , which lies at the heart of his homomorphism preservation theorem in the finite. • c K1 and c K2 satisfy the same FO sentences up to quantifier rank k, and",
